#. type: Block title
#: upstream/_versions/2.7/guides/writing-extensions.adoc:2303
#, no-wrap
msgid "Register a Bean Defining Annotation"
msgstr "アノテーションを定義する Bean の登録"

#. type: Plain text
#: upstream/_versions/2.7/guides/writing-extensions.adoc:2343
